    GT 4.0 Java WS Core : System Administrator's Guide
    Admin Guide


      Introduction

This guide contains advanced configuration information for system administrators
        working with Java WS Core. It provides references to information on procedures
        typically performed by system administrators, including installation, configuring,
        deploying, and testing the installation.

        This information is in addition to the basic Globus Toolkit prerequisite, overview, installation, security configuration instructions in the GT 4.0 System Administrator's Guide. Read through this guide before continuing!


